	<h1 class="title">Taylor Swift新歌又能在线听了，只不过这次要收钱</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">杨茜</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-03-26 08:30:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/7773/medium/7773.jpg?1436693408" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


